@serverPort = 3775

## --- Dead Letter Queue Retries ---

### Retry 1 dead letter (default) for GetAllDwellings projector
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetAllDwellings/components/dwellingReadModelProjector/dead-letters/retries

### Retry up to 10 dead letters for GetAllDwellings projector
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetAllDwellings/components/dwellingReadModelProjector/dead-letters/retries?limit=10

### Retry all dead letters for GetAllDwellings projector
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetAllDwellings/components/dwellingReadModelProjector/dead-letters/retries?limit=0

### Retry dead letters for GetCurrentDay projector
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetCurrentDay/components/currentDayReadModelProjector/dead-letters/retries

### Retry dead letters for GetWeekSymbol projector
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetWeekSymbol/components/weekSymbolReadModelProjector/dead-letters/retries

### Retry dead letters for GetArmyCreatures projector
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetArmyCreatures/components/creatureStackReadModelProjector/dead-letters/retries

### Retry dead letters for WhenWeekStartedThenProclaimWeekSymbol automation
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/Automation_WhenWeekStartedThenProclaimWeekSymbol/components/whenWeekStartedThenProclaimWeekSymbolProcessor/dead-letters/retries

### Retry dead letters for WhenWeekSymbolProclaimedThenIncreaseDwellingAvailableCreatures automation
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/Automation_WhenWeekSymbolProclaimedThenIncreaseDwellingAvailableCreatures/components/whenWeekSymbolProclaimedThenIncreaseDwellingAvailableCreaturesProcessor/dead-letters/retries

## --- Reset Event Processors ---

### Reset GetAllDwellings processor
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetAllDwellings/resets

### Reset GetCurrentDay processor
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetCurrentDay/resets

### Reset GetWeekSymbol processor
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetWeekSymbol/resets

### Reset GetArmyCreatures processor
POST http://localhost:{{serverPort}}/maintenance/event-processors/ReadModel_GetArmyCreatures/resets
